title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 06.02.08
description:
DEAD BEAT DAD WITH 7 KIDS:
    --------------------------
    Tito is 31 years old, has 5 children, and has 2 children on the way with 2 different women. Angela, pregnant with Tito&#039;s baby, is 7 month pregnant and homeless! Tito doesn&#039;t want to take care of Angela or his soon-to-be child because he says he only cares about himself. Kristi, also pregnant with Tito&#039;s baby, says that she loves him very much and has been letting him stay with her. Angela&#039;s mom Cindy comes out and says that she loves Angela but doesn&#039;t want her to stay with Tito. Steve can&#039;t understand why these women would want to be with Tito. Will Steve be able to convince Angela and Kristi to stay away from Tito?
